WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:04.972
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:05.944 --> 00:08.652
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.784 --> 00:13.792
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.816 --> 00:18.572
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.608 --> 00:22.636
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.640 --> 00:27.584
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.608 --> 00:30.880
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:30.904 --> 00:34.368
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.392 --> 00:39.640
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.640 --> 00:41.258
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.258 --> 00:44.736
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.760 --> 00:48.032
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.056 --> 00:53.728
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.752 --> 00:55.096
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.096 --> 00:58.432
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.456 --> 01:01.804
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:01.912 --> 01:07.109
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.109 --> 01:08.792
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.792 --> 01:12.192
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.216 --> 01:15.616
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.640 --> 01:21.216
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.240 --> 01:24.652
♪ I love you ♪

01:26.930 --> 01:27.720
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.720 --> 01:30.928
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 10=

01:30.952 --> 01:34.915
(Whether I'm Qiang Qingci
or Mo Qingcheng, I'm serious.)

01:34.939 --> 01:36.359
Sheng.

01:40.139 --> 01:43.919
He didn't lie to you.
He's really busy with his work.

01:44.100 --> 01:45.956
Then I better eat a bit more.

01:45.980 --> 01:48.115
Otherwise, I don't know
when the next meal with you will be.

01:48.139 --> 01:51.079
Next time… Let me think.

01:51.980 --> 01:54.236
How about two weeks from now?

01:54.260 --> 01:55.475
- Really?
- Really?

01:55.499 --> 01:56.995
If I don't work overtime.

01:57.019 --> 01:57.875
Then it's a deal.

01:57.899 --> 01:59.000
I'll wait for you.

02:01.459 --> 02:02.720
Try this.

02:06.619 --> 02:08.840
Is the rain outside getting heavier?

02:09.260 --> 02:11.639
Yes. It's really pouring out there.

02:12.019 --> 02:13.760
You can't go back now, right?

02:14.500 --> 02:17.040
Let's think about what to eat
for the late-night snack.

02:17.859 --> 02:19.435
No way. I have the early shift tomorrow.

02:19.459 --> 02:21.119
I have to go back tonight.

02:21.660 --> 02:23.199
The early shift?

02:23.940 --> 02:26.040
But I can stay a bit longer.

02:27.380 --> 02:28.679
What do you want to eat?

02:28.980 --> 02:30.356
Can I say it?

02:30.380 --> 02:31.636
Stop joking.

02:31.660 --> 02:34.399
It's pouring outside.
Grocery shopping is impossible for now.

02:34.980 --> 02:37.160
Wouldn't that be too much trouble?

02:37.260 --> 02:38.560
Would it?

02:38.619 --> 02:41.275
How about
I make some Yangzhou fried rice later?

02:41.299 --> 02:42.579
- I'll make a bit more.
- That's great!

02:42.579 --> 02:44.636
Can I take some with me?

02:44.660 --> 02:47.675
Sure, as long
as there are enough ingredients.

02:47.699 --> 02:49.555
Yangzhou fried rice is my favorite.

02:49.579 --> 02:50.619
I'm cooking the rice now.

02:50.619 --> 02:51.179
Just eat first.

02:51.179 --> 02:51.835
I'll help you.

02:51.859 --> 02:53.155
You don't know where the rice is.

02:53.179 --> 02:54.516
The food will be cold.

02:54.540 --> 02:55.760
Right.

02:57.780 --> 02:58.959
Go ahead and eat.

03:03.579 --> 03:04.799
Thank you.

03:06.019 --> 03:07.359
What for?

03:08.139 --> 03:11.119
For being responsive to them.

03:11.380 --> 03:14.480
Aren't they all your friends?
It's just a small favor.

03:14.980 --> 03:16.356
Seeing them eat so happily

03:16.380 --> 03:17.639
makes me happy too.

03:25.500 --> 03:30.036
Let's play Truth or Dare tonight.

03:30.060 --> 03:33.139
We'll draw cards to determine the order.

03:33.139 --> 03:35.739
The one who draws the largest card
is the loser,

03:35.739 --> 03:37.820
and we can ask him questions.
How about that?

03:37.820 --> 03:39.595
- Okay.
- Good idea.

03:39.619 --> 03:43.476
- Let's do it.
- Let's start with Mr. Mo.

03:43.500 --> 03:46.399
- Okay.
- Sheng.

03:51.940 --> 03:53.036
Wait a moment.

03:53.060 --> 03:55.835
As the person in charge of the studio,
I'd like to say something.

03:55.859 --> 03:57.715
It's raining heavily outside today,

03:57.739 --> 03:59.675
so we can't play Dare.

03:59.699 --> 04:03.019
We have to play Truth only.

04:03.019 --> 04:03.899
- Truth.
- Okay.

04:03.899 --> 04:06.160
We'll show our cards together
when I count to one.

04:06.540 --> 04:08.720
Three, two, one.

04:12.259 --> 04:16.319
Which one of you pursued the other?

04:19.780 --> 04:20.999
I pursued her.

04:23.499 --> 04:25.679
Alright, the second round.

04:31.140 --> 04:33.400
Three, two, one.

04:34.499 --> 04:36.835
Sheng got the largest card. I'll ask.

04:36.859 --> 04:41.040
Which one of you likes the other more?

04:46.980 --> 04:48.840
Hey, no cheating.

04:49.619 --> 04:51.676
I didn't speak just now.

04:51.700 --> 04:54.960
Okay, I'll let you pass. Next round.

04:58.100 --> 05:00.679
Three, two, one.

05:03.700 --> 05:05.080
Me?

05:06.299 --> 05:09.480
Where did you first meet?

05:10.859 --> 05:11.919
The supermarket.

05:14.220 --> 05:15.196
I see.

05:15.220 --> 05:16.919
- Let's do it again.
- Come on.

05:19.460 --> 05:21.400
Three, two, one.

05:21.859 --> 05:23.059
Sheng has the largest card.

05:23.059 --> 05:26.035
Wait. Why do we
always get the largest cards?

05:26.059 --> 05:27.559
Are you guys cheating?

05:28.179 --> 05:29.715
You have to admit defeat, Shengshengman.

05:29.739 --> 05:30.960
- Right.
- Right.

05:31.220 --> 05:32.319
I'll shuffle.

05:35.939 --> 05:36.499
It won't be me.

05:36.499 --> 05:38.840
- Okay.
- Come on.

05:42.220 --> 05:42.980
Look at you!

05:42.980 --> 05:48.840
- Did you fall for Sheng at first sight?
- Yes.

05:49.780 --> 05:52.116
- I knew it!
- I knew it!

05:52.140 --> 05:53.556
Now it's Sheng's turn.

05:53.580 --> 05:55.155
Did you ever kiss?

05:55.179 --> 05:56.220
Of course not.

05:56.220 --> 05:56.739
Three.

05:56.739 --> 06:01.020
When do you plan to kiss her?
Have you thought about it?

06:01.020 --> 06:01.956
Even secretly?

06:01.980 --> 06:03.520
Tell us.

06:05.900 --> 06:08.235
Go easy on her,
and let's play Dare for this round.

06:08.259 --> 06:09.259
No way.

06:09.259 --> 06:10.196
No.

06:10.220 --> 06:11.859
Alright, let them do that.

06:11.859 --> 06:13.636
Mr. Mo is our guest after all.

06:13.660 --> 06:15.020
No, I need to get an answer.

06:15.020 --> 06:18.340
- Think about the Yangzhou fried rice.
- Okay.

06:18.340 --> 06:19.460
You can do that.

06:19.460 --> 06:22.556
Okay, then. Can you sing?

06:22.580 --> 06:25.480
Since you're here,
you might as well sing a song.

06:25.540 --> 06:27.355
I'm just average at singing.

06:27.379 --> 06:28.595
- That's okay.
- That's okay.

06:28.619 --> 06:29.876
We are not picky listeners.

06:29.900 --> 06:31.355
And you are not a singer.

06:31.379 --> 06:32.900
Right, just pick any song.

06:32.900 --> 06:33.676
I'll play the guitar.

06:33.700 --> 06:34.996
I'll join you.

06:35.020 --> 06:36.919
No need. I'll do it myself.

06:38.819 --> 06:39.475
Okay.

06:39.499 --> 06:40.520
Okay.

06:44.619 --> 06:48.359
But I don't play very well.

06:48.660 --> 06:50.035
Just bear with my playing.

06:50.059 --> 06:52.280
- It's fine.
- It's fine.

07:00.350 --> 07:05.811
♪ We haven't met before that year ♪

07:07.454 --> 07:13.723
♪ Staring into the starry night ♪

07:14.686 --> 07:21.460
♪ We wonder who we'll
spend our lives with ♪

07:22.110 --> 07:27.579
♪ My thoughts constitute a dream ♪

07:29.438 --> 07:34.524
♪ We just met that year ♪

07:36.100 --> 07:38.400
Did you compose this song?

07:40.819 --> 07:42.280
Did you mention it to him?

07:43.678 --> 07:50.914
♪ Our paths are meant to cross ♪

07:51.230 --> 07:56.316
♪ In those years of youth and beauty ♪

07:58.558 --> 08:05.488
♪ When we suddenly turned around ♪

08:05.758 --> 08:10.876
♪ Geese were flying back home ♪

08:21.340 --> 08:24.440
I'm really sorry to trouble you
right before you leave.

08:24.779 --> 08:28.560
They remind me of the dubbing team
I used to be part of.

08:29.739 --> 08:31.759
Feng Yasong came from a poor family.

08:31.980 --> 08:34.115
When we first started working
at the hospital,

08:34.139 --> 08:35.960
he wouldn't eat at the cafeteria.

08:36.739 --> 08:40.080
Later, I would often make extra food
for him to take.

08:40.980 --> 08:43.080
Then he was really fortunate.

09:04.980 --> 09:06.759
This rain is heavier.

09:10.659 --> 09:12.115
There are only two umbrellas.

09:12.139 --> 09:14.196
How about you use mine?

09:14.220 --> 09:17.200
It's a bit cute, if you don't mind.

09:19.340 --> 09:20.480
It's okay.

09:23.779 --> 09:25.119
Then I'll go ahead.

09:27.420 --> 09:28.995
What's your relationship now?

09:29.019 --> 09:30.879
You even won't share an umbrella.

09:31.060 --> 09:34.119
We just started.

09:35.899 --> 09:37.879
Just started?

09:38.940 --> 09:40.556
You're finally admitting it.

09:40.580 --> 09:41.619
There's nothing to deny.

09:41.619 --> 09:42.436
There is.

09:42.460 --> 09:43.916
He's being quite obvious toward you.

09:43.940 --> 09:46.316
And you're being elusive toward him.

09:46.340 --> 09:49.359
That's understandable.
You are shy in front of us, right?

09:49.539 --> 09:51.916
Better hurry.
Don't you need to catch the last bus?

09:51.940 --> 09:52.999
Let's go.

09:54.340 --> 09:55.800
Watch your step.

10:14.379 --> 10:16.239
You guys chat. I'll wait over here.

10:18.023 --> 10:20.924
(Jiaodong University Station)

10:23.259 --> 10:25.076
Thank you for escorting me
back to school

10:25.100 --> 10:26.556
and for cooking for us.

10:26.580 --> 10:28.759
Isn't that a bit too formal?

10:29.859 --> 10:34.080
I mean, you shouldn't thank me,
given our relationship.

10:43.420 --> 10:46.560
Why not tell them who I am?

10:47.100 --> 10:50.595
You don't show up in front of people.

10:50.619 --> 10:53.039
I thought you wouldn't enjoy that.

10:55.820 --> 10:58.999
But they're your friends.
It's different.

11:01.739 --> 11:03.200
But...

11:04.180 --> 11:05.480
But what?

11:08.779 --> 11:13.720
What if we don't end up together?

11:13.940 --> 11:18.200
It's not good
to let others know who you are.

11:20.899 --> 11:22.440
Why are you laughing?

11:24.539 --> 11:28.359
What have I done today
to upset you so much?

11:29.420 --> 11:30.639
Not at all.

11:33.060 --> 11:36.519
Then why are you contemplating a breakup

11:37.100 --> 11:39.320
before I left?

11:43.899 --> 11:45.720
I said that casually.

11:46.980 --> 11:51.600
I am rational.

11:58.220 --> 12:00.080
Then let me say it again.

12:04.100 --> 12:05.440
I am serious.

12:06.739 --> 12:08.480
Whether I'm Qiang Qingci

12:10.460 --> 12:11.999
or Mo Qingcheng,

12:13.700 --> 12:15.119
I am serious.

12:17.888 --> 12:23.081
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

12:23.712 --> 12:27.061
♪ My heart is racing ♪

12:27.584 --> 12:32.138
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

12:36.019 --> 12:39.440
I don't know what to say.

12:41.619 --> 12:46.039
I've thought about it for a long time
and still don't know.

12:48.220 --> 12:51.960
I just feel like I'm dreaming.

12:53.420 --> 12:57.119
I'm not used to this.
I have no experience.

12:59.580 --> 13:03.440
What I said earlier
was just a hypothetical one.

13:05.139 --> 13:07.800
Because you have many fans.

13:07.859 --> 13:11.960
From your perspective, the fewer
people who know it, the better.

13:14.259 --> 13:15.960
I am also serious.

13:19.580 --> 13:20.759
I know.

13:28.940 --> 13:31.595
The last train is coming.
You should go quickly.

13:31.619 --> 13:33.515
It's hard to get a taxi here
when it's raining.

13:33.539 --> 13:36.920
Remember to send me a message.

13:40.659 --> 13:42.436
If I can't reply in time,

13:42.460 --> 13:44.200
it means I'm in the operating room.

13:44.379 --> 13:47.159
Or I'm in the outpatient clinic
or doing rounds.

13:48.139 --> 13:49.759
I'll reply when I see it.

13:54.574 --> 13:57.515
Keep it.
My friend and I can share an umbrella.

13:57.734 --> 13:59.391
There's a convenience store
at my destination.

13:59.415 --> 14:01.151
I'll buy another one then.

14:01.175 --> 14:02.310
With such heavy rain,

14:02.334 --> 14:05.114
it's easy for both of you
to get wet by sharing an umbrella.

14:06.935 --> 14:07.995
Okay then.

14:09.614 --> 14:11.874
Don't keep your friend waiting. Just go.

14:12.775 --> 14:16.594
- I'll go after you leave.
- Okay.

14:18.408 --> 14:21.916
(Jiaodong University Station)

14:28.318 --> 14:30.024
♪ I am with you ♪

14:30.024 --> 14:31.712
♪ I love you ♪

14:31.712 --> 14:35.144
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

14:35.144 --> 14:38.866
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

14:40.734 --> 14:42.915
Stop that. He has left.

14:44.614 --> 14:47.114
I was worried
he would miss the last train.

14:48.815 --> 14:50.395
Qiang Qingci lost.

14:51.815 --> 14:54.635
I said Qiang Qingci lost.

14:54.775 --> 14:57.755
You obviously like Mr. Mo more.

14:59.094 --> 15:00.275
Maybe.

15:04.454 --> 15:05.734
(Mo Qingcheng)
(I'm on the train.)

15:05.734 --> 15:07.354
Let's go. Hurry up.

15:11.974 --> 15:13.115
Go.

15:20.854 --> 15:23.470
Our school environment is pretty, right?

15:23.494 --> 15:26.474
Aren't you going to compliment it
after the tour?

15:28.614 --> 15:29.724
It is pretty.

15:38.255 --> 15:39.915
(Isn't he leaving?)

15:41.775 --> 15:43.675
Well, it's raining heavily.

15:44.055 --> 15:48.234
I'm afraid you might get wet
if I let you go now.

15:49.574 --> 15:53.190
Well, let's stay a little longer then.

15:53.214 --> 15:56.035
Okay. I have nothing else to do anyway.

16:05.295 --> 16:06.871
What do you do for a living?

16:06.895 --> 16:10.515
You seem fairly free, being able
to stay around my school for a day.

16:11.694 --> 16:14.994
I run my own company,
and I have pretty flexible time.

16:20.854 --> 16:21.854
What?

16:24.454 --> 16:25.954
Nothing.

16:26.494 --> 16:29.594
It's the first time I've met someone

16:29.775 --> 16:32.354
who compliments himself
for being capable.

16:33.454 --> 16:36.031
I'm actually not that capable.

16:36.055 --> 16:39.594
My company is not large,
and my annual income is enough to spend.

16:44.094 --> 16:46.994
It's also the first time
I've met someone who is not modest.

17:02.495 --> 17:05.191
Are you thinking of leaving?

17:05.215 --> 17:06.315
No.

17:07.455 --> 17:10.910
I noticed you've been
tapping the steering wheel.

17:10.934 --> 17:13.910
Usually, when I'm impatient,
I like to do the same thing.

17:13.934 --> 17:16.354
No, I am wondering

17:17.215 --> 17:19.315
if you are usually very busy.

17:19.934 --> 17:22.231
Sometimes, I want to message you.

17:22.255 --> 17:25.511
But I feel a bit shy,

17:25.535 --> 17:27.715
being afraid of disturbing you.

17:27.894 --> 17:31.110
I'm not busy.
You can contact me anytime.

17:31.134 --> 17:32.195
Really?

17:34.255 --> 17:39.154
Okay. I'm usually free as well.

17:39.295 --> 17:43.350
Except sometimes
when I'm in the recording studio.

17:43.374 --> 17:45.114
I'm not busy at any other time.

17:45.894 --> 17:48.594
Okay, let's stay in touch.

17:48.695 --> 17:50.195
Okay.

17:56.614 --> 17:58.910
Sheng is back.

17:58.934 --> 18:00.795
Well, goodbye then.

18:06.574 --> 18:08.555
Sheng. Sheng.

18:10.495 --> 18:11.711
Where is your umbrella?

18:11.735 --> 18:12.795
I forgot.

18:13.215 --> 18:15.434
Let's go. It's raining heavily.

18:23.540 --> 18:27.900
(Emergency Outpatient)

18:30.346 --> 18:36.156
(Children's Emergency Service Desk)

18:40.094 --> 18:40.951
Thank you, doctor.

18:40.975 --> 18:41.870
Thank you.

18:41.894 --> 18:42.995
You're welcome.

18:43.455 --> 18:45.031
What are you doing?

18:45.055 --> 18:47.275
I want to see what he looks like.

18:47.535 --> 18:48.431
I'm sorry.

18:48.455 --> 18:48.991
It's alrighty.

18:49.015 --> 18:50.231
She is naughty.

18:50.255 --> 18:52.310
Hey, let me tell you a secret.

18:52.334 --> 18:54.590
All doctors look alike.

18:54.614 --> 18:56.114
Only their eyes differ.

18:57.134 --> 18:58.590
Next time you come to the hospital

18:58.614 --> 18:59.791
and see someone like me

18:59.815 --> 19:01.995
who covers everything but their eyes

19:02.055 --> 19:04.114
and wears a nameplate like this
on their chest,

19:04.455 --> 19:07.354
that's someone who can treat you,
got it?

19:09.215 --> 19:11.854
Doctor, please look at my child first.

19:11.854 --> 19:13.535
He suddenly fainted.
I don't know what happened.

19:13.535 --> 19:14.310
- Come in.
- Okay.

19:14.334 --> 19:16.795
What's happening?

19:18.614 --> 19:19.991
I've been waiting in line.

19:20.015 --> 19:21.271
How could you let him in first

19:21.295 --> 19:23.070
without even asking me?

19:23.094 --> 19:24.110
It's urgent.

19:24.134 --> 19:26.354
Didn't you see
the child was unconscious?

19:26.735 --> 19:28.070
Is their time more valuable

19:28.094 --> 19:29.674
than mine?

19:29.894 --> 19:31.910
We should all follow the rules
and wait our turn.

19:31.934 --> 19:32.870
I am really sorry.

19:32.894 --> 19:34.031
My child is unconscious.

19:34.055 --> 19:35.674
Please see him first.

19:35.775 --> 19:36.495
Move. Come with me.

19:36.495 --> 19:38.431
The father can come in.

19:38.455 --> 19:39.914
What's going on?

19:40.015 --> 19:41.955
Can't you let them save the child first?

19:42.654 --> 19:43.854
What department are you in?

19:43.854 --> 19:46.315
Is this your business to meddle in?

19:47.215 --> 19:50.275
Life matters most. Being unconscious
could be life-threatening.

19:51.295 --> 19:52.110
Alright.

19:52.134 --> 19:54.174
- That child is in danger.
- Let go.

19:54.174 --> 19:55.271
We can wait.

19:55.295 --> 19:56.870
Let them see the doctor first.

19:56.894 --> 19:59.630
- Mother, stay away.
- Right. Aren't we all waiting?

19:59.654 --> 20:00.854
They went in because it was urgent.

20:00.854 --> 20:03.310
There are always lots of patients
in pediatrics.

20:03.334 --> 20:04.830
Let's try to understand each other.

20:04.854 --> 20:06.695
Dr. Liu saw over a hundred outpatients
during the day

20:06.695 --> 20:07.910
before emergency cases at night.

20:07.934 --> 20:09.590
That was an emergency.

20:09.614 --> 20:11.015
Everyone, please go away.

20:11.015 --> 20:12.334
They wouldn't even queue properly.

20:12.334 --> 20:14.354
Please go away.

20:16.334 --> 20:18.191
Dr. Mo, what brings you here?

20:18.215 --> 20:19.671
I'm here for a consultation.

20:19.695 --> 20:21.634
- Then I'll get back to work.
- Okay.

20:23.266 --> 20:27.508
(Girl's Dorm Building 3)

20:34.015 --> 20:36.195
What's the matter with you two?

20:36.775 --> 20:37.914
Please take a seat.

20:46.815 --> 20:49.511
Do you have anything to say?

20:49.535 --> 20:51.795
Opportunities wait for no one.

21:01.015 --> 21:05.235
He and I...

21:05.295 --> 21:06.590
Who? Say his name.

21:06.614 --> 21:08.555
He is not a nobody. Say his name.

21:21.414 --> 21:22.795
- Say it.
- Say it.

21:26.975 --> 21:28.515
I'm with him now.

21:40.654 --> 21:42.834
Pinch my face
to let me see if it's real.

21:42.894 --> 21:44.275
It is real.

21:44.455 --> 21:45.715
Ouch.

21:46.975 --> 21:48.191
Sheng.

21:48.215 --> 21:49.055
Sheng.

21:49.055 --> 21:50.894
You're with my idol now.

21:50.894 --> 21:53.114
You are finally not single anymore.

22:15.610 --> 22:17.975
(Hospitalization Department, Emergency)

22:17.975 --> 22:19.191
Is it real?

22:19.215 --> 22:20.070
Yes.

22:20.094 --> 22:21.434
He really did that?

22:21.854 --> 22:23.195
Impressive.

22:24.374 --> 22:26.031
We were just talking about you.

22:26.055 --> 22:29.630
I heard you did a good deed
in pediatrics today.

22:29.654 --> 22:30.995
Are you okay?

22:31.574 --> 22:32.471
I'm fine.

22:32.495 --> 22:34.590
Pediatrics is full of worrying parents.

22:34.614 --> 22:37.471
It's easy for a couple of them
to get anxious.

22:37.495 --> 22:40.630
I've heard their department hasn't
filled all their positions this year.

22:40.654 --> 22:42.150
There will be fewer doctors later.

22:42.174 --> 22:43.910
Eventually,
when there are no pediatricians,

22:43.934 --> 22:45.834
everyone will know
how precious they are.

22:46.574 --> 22:48.074
It's tough for everyone.

22:48.295 --> 22:50.431
You haven't eaten, right?

22:50.455 --> 22:52.830
While you are not busy,
you should eat now.

22:52.854 --> 22:53.995
Good idea.

22:54.775 --> 22:57.195
No need. I brought you food.

22:57.255 --> 22:59.154
I've heated it up. Go ahead and eat it.

23:01.535 --> 23:03.590
Then you eat. I'm going back to work.

23:03.614 --> 23:05.035
Dr. Mo, I'm leaving.

23:08.455 --> 23:11.751
All the hunger I've suffered
is worth it when I can eat

23:11.775 --> 23:13.154
what you cook.

23:15.174 --> 23:17.231
By the way,
help me look at this medical record.

23:17.255 --> 23:18.515
Meanwhile, I'll eat.

23:21.775 --> 23:22.914
What's wrong?

23:23.695 --> 23:26.830
Nothing, maybe I got a cold.

23:26.854 --> 23:28.711
Got a cold?

23:28.735 --> 23:30.870
I'll find you some medicine.

23:30.894 --> 23:34.751
As a doctor, don't you know
how important your health is?

23:34.775 --> 23:36.434
I'll brew a packet for you.

23:36.934 --> 23:38.755
- Thanks.
- Don't mention it.

23:39.392 --> 23:43.228
(Jiayuan)

24:01.495 --> 24:03.795
- What are you doing?
- Let's talk.

24:07.094 --> 24:09.154
You talk, and I'll listen.

24:09.574 --> 24:11.910
I don't see you often in this place.

24:11.934 --> 24:14.955
We are almost becoming strangers.

24:15.495 --> 24:17.874
You talk, and I'll listen.

24:18.775 --> 24:19.874
Alright.

24:21.854 --> 24:24.711
How many times did you
meet Shengshengman

24:24.735 --> 24:26.070
before you started pursuing her?

24:26.094 --> 24:27.515
Wasn't it too impulsive?

24:29.334 --> 24:31.031
I think when it comes to love,

24:31.055 --> 24:33.715
you need to slow down
to get to know her.

24:34.295 --> 24:35.315
Well,

24:35.654 --> 24:38.235
you need to know her perspective, right?

24:38.695 --> 24:40.471
For example, her views on love,

24:40.495 --> 24:41.574
her values,

24:41.574 --> 24:42.951
and her outlook on life.

24:42.975 --> 24:44.515
You have to know all of these.

24:44.695 --> 24:47.751
And you also need to know
her attitude towards her parents,

24:47.775 --> 24:49.475
towards kids,

24:49.614 --> 24:50.870
and towards small animals.

24:50.894 --> 24:53.431
You can't be too impulsive, right?

24:53.455 --> 24:55.334
You not only need to know what she likes

24:55.334 --> 24:57.630
but also what she dislikes.

24:57.654 --> 25:00.394
You have to know
whether she doesn't like

25:01.775 --> 25:03.715
those who are too muscular,

25:04.174 --> 25:08.315
or men with small eyes,

25:08.535 --> 25:12.751
or men who are too old, right?

25:12.775 --> 25:14.634
Do you have someone in mind?

25:15.934 --> 25:16.711
No.

25:16.735 --> 25:17.630
I don't.

25:17.654 --> 25:19.114
Aren't we talking about you?

25:24.775 --> 25:27.511
If you're unsure,
I suggest you wait until another day.

25:27.535 --> 25:28.711
No, let's talk today.

25:28.735 --> 25:31.791
Just a bit more.

25:31.815 --> 25:33.475
Don't sleep. It's still early.

26:20.894 --> 26:22.914
Come on. Let's talk.

26:24.234 --> 26:25.475
About perspectives.

26:25.614 --> 26:26.471
No. Just sleep.

26:26.495 --> 26:28.195
No more talking.

26:36.334 --> 26:37.854
Get up.

26:37.854 --> 26:40.471
(Girl's Dorm Building 3)
My boyfriend is treating you to snacks.

26:40.495 --> 26:41.874
Here you are.

26:41.934 --> 26:43.074
So many.

26:44.055 --> 26:46.870
Sheng, here you are.

26:46.894 --> 26:48.674
Thank you.

26:49.215 --> 26:50.590
You and your boyfriend

26:50.614 --> 26:53.231
make me believe
that love is still worth believing in.

26:53.255 --> 26:54.751
Do you want to be in love too?

26:54.775 --> 26:56.870
Why don't you hurry up
and find a boyfriend?

26:56.894 --> 26:59.550
(Heading to the hospital. See you.)
Love can bring joy.

26:59.574 --> 27:01.271
(He should get off work now.)

27:01.295 --> 27:03.475
(Why hasn't he sent me any messages?)

27:29.255 --> 27:30.475
Wake up.

27:31.174 --> 27:32.434
It's ten AM.

27:32.654 --> 27:33.755
Get up now.

27:35.614 --> 27:37.394
Pour me a glass of hot water, please.

27:37.854 --> 27:38.955
What's wrong?

27:39.815 --> 27:41.354
I'm feeling a bit unwell.

27:43.295 --> 27:44.271
You got a cold?

27:44.295 --> 27:46.434
Why didn't you
cover yourself with a quilt?

27:46.614 --> 27:47.991
Next time, just sleep in your own room.

27:48.015 --> 27:49.755
Then I can cover myself with a quilt.

28:01.495 --> 28:02.711
The water is here.

28:02.735 --> 28:03.795
Thanks.

28:06.894 --> 28:09.755
You seem to have a fever.
Shall I take you to the hospital?

28:10.455 --> 28:11.995
I'll just lie down for a bit.

28:12.215 --> 28:14.914
I'm off work today.
I've taken sick leave.

28:15.854 --> 28:17.390
If it gets worse,

28:17.414 --> 28:19.644
I'll get checked
when I go to work tomorrow.

28:21.614 --> 28:22.715
Alright.

28:22.775 --> 28:23.711
Drink the water.

28:23.735 --> 28:25.715
- Do you have any medicine?
- Yes.

28:25.854 --> 28:27.874
I'll read the script.
Call me if you need me.

28:28.614 --> 28:30.035
Keep warm.

28:36.612 --> 28:38.780
(Heading to the hospital. See you.)

28:41.934 --> 28:43.594
What are you thinking about?

28:47.215 --> 28:48.310
Look at her.

28:48.334 --> 28:50.991
Ever since she was with my idol,

28:51.015 --> 28:52.590
there has been nothing else on her mind.

28:52.614 --> 28:55.910
But the image of that man.

28:55.934 --> 28:57.815
- One mustn't get lost in love.
- You will lose yourself.

28:57.815 --> 28:58.975
It's dangerous.

28:58.975 --> 28:59.695
Gu Sheng.

28:59.695 --> 29:02.910
I'm just worried
he's oversleeping from working late.

29:02.934 --> 29:05.114
I wonder if it's good
to send a message now.

29:08.392 --> 29:09.870
I'll stop staring at my phone, okay?

29:09.894 --> 29:11.975
No. What if your boyfriend
slips through your fingers?

29:11.975 --> 29:14.515
What a pity that would be.

29:14.975 --> 29:16.511
He's been pretty nice to you.

29:16.535 --> 29:17.795
That's right.

29:19.414 --> 29:21.315
What exactly do you want?

29:22.455 --> 29:25.150
Of course, I want you to be happy.

29:25.174 --> 29:26.834
Of course.

29:29.535 --> 29:30.590
Where are you going?

29:30.614 --> 29:32.215
To see Mr. Qiang?

29:32.215 --> 29:33.634
Highly likely.

29:34.134 --> 29:35.830
I'm going to the library.

29:35.854 --> 29:36.495
Have you forgotten?

29:36.495 --> 29:38.674
We promised to help the teacher
organize books.

29:39.414 --> 29:41.755
Right. Sheng, wait for me.

29:56.255 --> 29:57.475
Zhou Zheng?

29:59.854 --> 30:01.594
Z-Zhou Zheng?

30:22.094 --> 30:24.275
These two books go over there as well.
Thank you.

30:31.134 --> 30:34.795
By the way, Sheng,
how is your thesis coming along?

30:35.455 --> 30:38.031
It's almost done.
I just want to make some adjustments.

30:38.055 --> 30:40.114
But I haven't figured out
how to adjust it yet.

30:40.215 --> 30:41.830
Really?

30:41.854 --> 30:44.515
Our top student also has times
when she's stumped?

30:45.455 --> 30:46.231
Xiaoxing.

30:46.255 --> 30:48.070
Come help me decide
where to put this book.

30:48.094 --> 30:50.315
Right, I forgot to tell you. Which one?

30:51.894 --> 30:53.634
I thought you weren't coming today.

30:54.334 --> 30:56.795
It was the task assigned by the teacher.
I would come.

30:57.535 --> 30:59.074
Are you stuck with your thesis?

31:00.255 --> 31:04.315
If you have time,
maybe we can discuss it together.

31:04.535 --> 31:05.390
Sure.

31:05.414 --> 31:06.995
How about today?

31:09.654 --> 31:10.334
I'm free today.

31:10.334 --> 31:11.674
(Off Key)
(Are you okay?)

31:12.374 --> 31:14.791
I'll give you a message
when I've thought about it.

31:14.815 --> 31:16.550
Okay, I'll wait for your message.

31:16.574 --> 31:18.275
- Goodbye.
- Bye.

31:21.735 --> 31:23.590
(Yes. What's wrong?)

31:23.614 --> 31:25.350
(I noticed
that you haven't posted on Weibo.)

31:25.374 --> 31:27.874
(I thought you were affected
by those posts.)

31:28.574 --> 31:30.191
(Fame attracts criticism.)

31:30.215 --> 31:32.634
(Hang in there, Shengshengman.)

31:37.806 --> 31:39.495
(Comments)

31:39.495 --> 31:40.975
(From a professional perspective, )

31:40.975 --> 31:43.471
(Shengshengman's composition
is just average.)

31:43.495 --> 31:47.070
(I don't understand
why it is said she is talented.)

31:47.094 --> 31:49.390
(I can't believe Qiang Qingci
is recommending her.)

31:49.414 --> 31:51.394
(What a bandwagon jumper!)

31:55.695 --> 31:57.874
Are you not feeling well?

31:58.695 --> 32:01.715
No, maybe I'm just hungry.

32:02.374 --> 32:03.914
Then let's go eat together.

32:05.455 --> 32:07.830
By the way, I saw the class leader
looking for you just now.

32:07.854 --> 32:09.074
Is something up?

32:10.455 --> 32:12.755
It's about the thesis.

32:14.455 --> 32:16.074
Just the thesis?

32:16.574 --> 32:18.711
Let's go to eat.

32:18.735 --> 32:20.511
A full belly solves all worries.

32:20.535 --> 32:22.914
I want to have
minced pork and vermicelli casserole.

32:23.574 --> 32:24.755
Wait.

32:25.495 --> 32:28.674
You don't look right.

32:28.735 --> 32:30.431
Who upsets you?

32:30.455 --> 32:32.475
Tell me, and I'll stand up for you.

32:37.094 --> 32:40.114
I just saw some unpleasant posts

32:40.174 --> 32:46.074
and got a bit affected emotionally.

32:46.775 --> 32:48.912
(Mo Qingcheng)
It's those online posts about you?

32:48.936 --> 32:50.310
- Sheng...
- Help me with this.

32:50.334 --> 32:51.471
I need to take this call.

32:51.495 --> 32:52.555
I...

32:52.614 --> 32:53.634
Hello?

32:57.255 --> 32:58.874
I just took a nap

32:59.614 --> 33:01.235
and haven't fully woken up yet.

33:01.574 --> 33:03.434
I'll sleep for another two hours

33:03.894 --> 33:05.191
before calling you, okay?

33:05.215 --> 33:07.195
Are you sick?

33:09.255 --> 33:12.195
I have a bit
of a sore throat and a fever.

33:12.455 --> 33:14.955
Did you take your temperature?

33:17.255 --> 33:18.394
Yes, I did.

33:18.455 --> 33:22.074
Then maybe you should
sleep a little more.

33:22.295 --> 33:25.834
- I'll call you when I wake up.
- Bye.

33:32.094 --> 33:33.114
Sheng,

33:33.414 --> 33:35.634
don't be upset
over things on the internet.

33:38.374 --> 33:40.735
It's not like that. I have to go now.

33:40.735 --> 33:42.134
I'm almost done here.
Go back when you finish.

33:42.134 --> 33:44.434
Wait. I... The books...

33:59.880 --> 34:02.172
(Mo Qingcheng)

34:02.454 --> 34:04.675
(He should still be asleep.)

34:14.655 --> 34:18.715
What's wrong? Forgot your access card?

34:19.735 --> 34:21.950
My boyfriend is sleeping.

34:21.974 --> 34:23.874
I'm afraid calling him will wake him up.

34:24.175 --> 34:25.071
Come on in.

34:25.095 --> 34:25.870
Thank you.

34:25.894 --> 34:27.755
Madam, let me carry them for you.

34:27.934 --> 34:29.155
Thank you so much.

34:31.334 --> 34:32.271
Thank you.

34:32.295 --> 34:33.474
Thank you.

34:37.934 --> 34:39.715
Which floor?

34:40.454 --> 34:41.994
The 16th floor as well.

34:42.854 --> 34:44.430
What a coincidence!

34:44.454 --> 34:47.354
Who is your boyfriend?

34:49.135 --> 34:52.914
Is it Dr. Mo who doesn't like to talk?

34:53.135 --> 34:56.034
Doctor is good. We've arrived.

34:58.135 --> 34:59.910
Give them to me. I live right there.

34:59.934 --> 35:01.671
No worries. I can carry them for you.

35:01.695 --> 35:02.994
Thank you.

35:13.615 --> 35:14.751
Give them to me.

35:14.775 --> 35:16.434
Please take care.

35:16.894 --> 35:18.470
Go find Dr. Mo quickly.

35:18.494 --> 35:19.715
Thank you.

35:20.175 --> 35:21.195
Goodbye.

35:59.135 --> 36:01.434
(I hope he's not delirious with fever.)

36:12.695 --> 36:14.075
Why did you come?

36:15.295 --> 36:16.715
Are you okay?

36:20.334 --> 36:21.514
Come in first.

36:27.215 --> 36:28.591
Here are the slippers.

36:28.615 --> 36:30.834
I'll go into the room first.
I'm not wearing much.

37:15.054 --> 37:18.195
Are you still feeling unwell?

37:18.334 --> 37:20.434
Do you want to go to the hospital?

37:26.934 --> 37:30.275
Lie down and rest for a bit.

37:30.494 --> 37:32.715
I'll get you some hot water in a moment.

37:37.815 --> 37:40.394
Aren't you cold in a skirt?

37:41.255 --> 37:43.791
It was quite warm
when I left in the morning.

37:43.815 --> 37:45.195
It's not cold for me.

37:45.255 --> 37:47.191
How about
I get you a pair of sports pants?

37:47.215 --> 37:49.115
There's a problem with the heating here.

37:49.974 --> 37:51.271
It's not very warm.

37:51.295 --> 37:53.910
Just lie down
and take a good rest first.

37:53.934 --> 37:56.994
You are the patient here.
Just ignore me.

38:31.374 --> 38:33.315
Have you taken the medicine?

38:42.575 --> 38:44.315
Why is it still so hot?

38:56.414 --> 38:58.315
Why are your hands so cold?

39:02.695 --> 39:05.115
I wanted to tell you last time.

39:06.175 --> 39:10.235
In winter,
you must wear skirts less often.

39:10.615 --> 39:12.444
It'll be better for your health.

39:13.334 --> 39:14.874
You must keep warm.

39:21.334 --> 39:25.034
What color is your towel?

39:26.054 --> 39:28.755
Let me wet it and help you cool down.

39:29.295 --> 39:30.554
It's white.

40:34.313 --> 40:36.220
(38 degrees)

41:18.615 --> 41:22.394
Staying together in a room
can be contagious.

41:23.454 --> 41:24.834
Maybe

41:29.615 --> 41:31.434
you should go out and sit for a while.

41:34.175 --> 41:37.514
It's okay. I'll keep you company.

41:38.575 --> 41:39.795
Just go.

41:41.215 --> 41:43.115
I'm here to see you.

41:43.334 --> 41:45.954
I'm the doctor. Listen to me.

41:46.414 --> 41:50.354
Well, this towel...

41:53.894 --> 41:56.994
I will use it later.

42:57.476 --> 43:02.332
(A Lifetime in Jiangnan)

43:33.295 --> 43:35.155
No wonder I'm hungry.

44:01.534 --> 44:02.834
This is delicious too.

44:22.295 --> 44:23.635
You're awake.

44:43.806 --> 44:49.267
♪ We haven't met before that year ♪

44:50.910 --> 44:57.179
♪ Staring into the starry night ♪

44:58.142 --> 45:04.916
♪ We wonder who we'll
spend our lives with ♪

45:05.566 --> 45:11.035
♪ My thoughts constitute a dream ♪

45:21.854 --> 45:27.067
♪ We just met that year ♪

45:29.224 --> 45:35.207
♪ Fate brought us closer ♪

45:36.573 --> 45:43.329
♪ Our paths are meant to cross ♪

45:43.711 --> 45:49.829
♪ In those years of youth and beauty ♪

45:51.071 --> 45:57.692
♪ When we suddenly turned around ♪

45:58.207 --> 46:05.586
♪ Geese were flying back home ♪

46:11.167 --> 46:17.846
♪ The moment I meet you ♪

46:18.272 --> 46:24.918
♪ I know you're the one I want ♪

46:25.631 --> 46:32.409
♪ No need to prove our love in a hurry ♪

46:32.895 --> 46:40.895
♪ Because it will last forever ♪
